Just One Boss — GameTank / gtlua port
=====================================

This is a fan port/adaptation of the game "Just One Boss" by bridgs
(ayla nonsense), originally released as a PICO-8 cartridge:

    https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?tid=30767

The original "Just One Boss" is licensed by its author under the
Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International
License (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0).

In keeping with that license, this GameTank port — including the
re-expressed game logic, the transcribed sprite sheet, and the
transcribed tracker/sound data derived from the original cart — is
released under the SAME license:

    Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0
    International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)

    https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/

